  <title>Menu bar visibility</title>

<!-- Use <steps>! -->

  <p>If you want to hide the menu bar in <app>Terminal</app>, go to
  <guiseq><gui style="menu">View</gui><gui style="menuitem">Show
  Menubar</gui></guiseq>.  Alternatively, you can access this option by right
  clicking anywhere inside the <app>Terminal</app> and select from the menu,
  <gui style="menuitem">Show Menubar</gui>.</p>

  <note style="tip">
    <p>To enable the menubar by default in all <app>Terminal</app> windows you
    open, go to <guiseq><gui style="menu">Edit</gui><gui
    style="menuitem">Preferences</gui><gui style="tab">General</gui></guiseq>
    and select <gui>Show menubar by default in new terminals</gui>.</p>
  </note>

